=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好低賤<br />\n每次我有少少要求<br />\n都會比佢地圍著嚟鬧同駁回<br />\n中學成長期只係得菜同魚食<br />\n原本好肥嘅我變左排骨<br />\n宜家連間房都無<br />\n但係兩個家姐有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮就咪生啦<br />\n女富養男窮養<br />\n當我狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4023a6a1b5b3378e50741b3dc80340ff8dc1a966","tid":39832,"uid":64413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好憎，因為做左20年人都仲味有間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來i'm not alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6b1e3d7f2dd0d7c304220a7adda73fc98e52c4","tid":39832,"uid":64413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係屋企地位好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好低賤<br />\n每次我有少少要求<br />\n都會比佢地圍著嚟鬧同駁回<br />\n中學成長期只係得菜同魚食<br />\n原本好肥嘅我變左排骨<br />\n宜家連間房都無<br />\n但係兩個家姐有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮就咪生啦<br />\n女富養男窮養<br />\n當我狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨生大左都要養返父母 同樣道理"},{"pid":"cdb1ff53ecc23fc57637e76d642861ae3c5de91d","tid":39832,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:10:13.000Z","msg":"我都好撚憎我老豆 所以搬左出黎住"},{"pid":"7ac97ae16d4323752e2c0737ca2e7cb608ffaf65","tid":39832,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係屋企地位好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好低賤<br />\n每次我有少少要求<br />\n都會比佢地圍著嚟鬧同駁回<br />\n中學成長期只係得菜同魚食<br />\n原本好肥嘅我變左排骨<br />\n宜家連間房都無<br />\n但係兩個家姐有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮就咪生啦<br />\n女富養男窮養<br />\n當我狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨生大左都要養返父母 同樣道理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌第時我出嚟做野咪又係我養老豆老母<br />\n嗰2條港女番左咁多年工一個仙都無比<br />\n其中一個仲要比人中出即飛<br />\n生左個仔放係屋企養<br />\n家陣屋企好大咩<br />\n以佢地2個年紀都應該嫁人啦<br />\n到宜家仲未搵到人埋單<br />\n佢地一日未嫁<br />\n我一日都要同老豆老母一間房訓<br />\n受盡佢地啲鼻鼾聲轟炸落耳仔度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21be6efe2a6bd8e874c44d361fe9b201ca4fb819","tid":39832,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好憎，因為做左20年人都仲味有間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來i'm not alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連床都無 點睇"},{"pid":"9e70f4ea690e8155644d1243eec47f89271160cc","tid":39832,"uid":64413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我好憎，因為做左20年人都仲味有間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來i'm not alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連床都無 點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我讓個腳位俾你"},{"pid":"a548caaf2c12eb54b46752e22c7659674b7ea6eb","tid":39832,"uid":35077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7315764d361fa711cf7cd961a346beb6efbeeee6","tid":39832,"uid":64413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"尤其是我係全屋企最細<br />\n乜都管7住唒 拖都唔俾拍 佢2個米又係我呢啲年紀開始拍拖？<br />\n中小都係讀女校 社交都可以話冇<br />\n老斗老母仲要24/7係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18年黎房都冇間 我隻龜都有個缸啦 一啲自己空間私穩都冇<br />\n落街先抖到啖氣 DSE開始stress eating <br />\n仲要一坐底就同你講你有幾廢幾差 我都知鬼叫你地咁中意困住你個女？<br />\n話做咩要生個仔激自己又害自己真係dllm 咁你學咩人生仔啊買隻狗米算囉 又識氹你開心又唔洗交學費 唔中意又可以隨時掉落街<br />\n我從來都唔會同屋企人講我有啲咩唔開心 傾條毛咩？一講完佢又話自己幾辛苦供書教學點點點我唔知足 仆街乜撚都係我嘅錯<br />\n<br />\n其 實 我 早 就 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天收</span>"}]}